                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-820" type="surname" value="CLIFTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-820" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM CLIFTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 50.) On the 17th of Feb. I received from Mrs. Weeks this half-crown.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
